    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "yo i just finished replacing the brake pads on my 2018 camry but every time i test drive it i get this really annoying high-pitched squealing sound coming from the front left side. not sure if i messed something up or if it's just a bad sensor or something. what should i check first?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
